===========================================================================
Advanced engine needed  : ZDoom and its spinoffs that support DECORATE
Primary purpose         : Single + coop play
===========================================================================
Title                   : Nemesis Hellsmith
Filename                : nemesis_hellsmith002fix.pk3
Release date            : April 28, 2019
Authors                 : Jon Armst (hellsmith1) and Larry Collins (Empyre)
Email Address           : jonsnascar@gmail.com and empyre65@gmail.com

Description             : Adds 5 new minotaur-based monsters that replace the
						  Cyberdemon: the Apprentice, the Hellsmith,
						  the Freezemotaur, the Supremotaur, and of course,
						  the Nemesis Hellsmith himself.  It also adds 4 new
						  weapons: Flak Cannon, Big Lightning Gun (BLG),
						  Stingray, and Legendry Unmaker.

Additional Credits to   : See the CREDITS lump.

===========================================================================
* What is included *

New levels              : 0
Sounds                  : Yes
Music                   : No
Graphics                : Yes
Dehacked/BEX Patch      : No
Demos                   : No
Other                   : DECORATE, SNDINFO
Other files required    : Complex-Doom with LCA, _OR_ the complete CF package
						  (see Play Instructions in the WADINFO in
						  nemesis_hellsmith_cf_patch002.wad), _OR_ the comprete
						  True CF package (see Play Instructions in the WADINFO in
						  nemesis_hellsmith_truecf_patch002.wad).


* Play Information *

NOTE: This will not work by itself.  It depends on Complex Doom and LCA to work.
Also, the patches for Complex Doom and for LCA are obsolete and no longer needed.

Game                    : Doom 2 or Doom
Map #                   : None
Single Player           : Designed for
Cooperative 2-4 Player  : Designed for
Deathmatch 2-4 Player   : No
Other game styles       : None
Difficulty Settings     : N/A


* Construction *

Base                    : Based on the Hellsmith and Apprentice available at Realm667.
Build Time              : Many hours over the course of several months.
Editor(s) used          : Slade 3 and GIMP-2.8 
Known Bugs              : none known, but please tell us of any you find
May Not Run With...     : non-ZDoom-based ports, and ZDaemon and Odamex,
                          because of the DECORATE code


