***** Changelog *****

Changes in nemesis_hellsmith002fix.pk3:

 - Fixed all known sprite conflicts with CD, LCA, and CF.
 - Replaced ammo types with their replacements from LCA.
 - Incorporated some, but not all, of the changes made in
cf_txs_cw_patch1.4.1_custom_complete.pk3.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Changes in nemesis_hellsmith002.pk3:

 - Made this pk3 depend on Complex Doom and LCA, using some code, sprites, and
 sounds from those pk3s, and not including them inside this pk3.
 - Added 4 weapons: the Flak Cannon, the Big Lightning Gun (BLG), the Stingray,
and the Legendary Unmaker
 - Cleaned up some unused or duplicate code, sounds, and sprites.
 - Added a song that plays when the Nemesis Hellsmith seees a player.
 - Added GLDEFS and DECALDEF to make everything look better.
 - Updated the CF patch (see changelog there) and added the True CF patch.
 - Added the new weapons to the drop-lists for included monsters, and made them
sometimes appear instad of the normal Complex Doom weapons.
